<darkcolour>A6416E</darkcolour><section><title>Pronoun &lt;I&gt;one/ones&lt;/I&gt;</title><sectiontitle>Don't repeat a noun in an answer. Use &lt;I&gt;one&lt;/I&gt;. We usually use &lt;I&gt;one&lt;/I&gt; after &lt;I&gt;this, that&lt;/I&gt; or an adjective.</sectiontitle><titlesound>ELEMGRAM_7_1_1.mp3</titlesound><text1>Do you like the old &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;chair?&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;</text1><sound1>ELEMGRAM_7_1_2.mp3</sound1><text1a>No, I like the new &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;one.&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;</text1a><text2>Do you want this &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;pizza?&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;</text2><sound2>ELEMGRAM_7_1_3.mp3</sound2><text2a>No, I want that &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;one.&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;</text2a><titlesound2>ELEMGRAM_7_1_4.mp3</titlesound2><sectiontitle2>Use &lt;I&gt;ones&lt;/I&gt; to replace plural nouns. We can use &lt;I&gt;ones&lt;/I&gt; after &lt;I&gt;these&lt;/I&gt; or &lt;I&gt;those&lt;/I&gt; or an adjective.</sectiontitle2><text3>Do you like the black &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;shoes&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;?</text3><sound3>ELEMGRAM_7_1_5.mp3</sound3><text3a>No, I like the brown &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;ones.&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;</text3a><text4>I want these &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;shoes&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;.</text4><sound4>ELEMGRAM_7_1_6.mp3</sound4><text4a>I want those &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;ones.&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;</text4a></section></grammar>